<div class="container">
    <div class="page-content">
        <div class="page-meta-info">
            <span class="category-link">
                <a href="/category/<%= page.category_slug %>"><%= page.category_name %></a>
            </span>
            <span class="date"><%= new Date(page.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %></span>
            <span class="views"><%= page.views %> views</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><%= page.content %></p>
            
            <!-- Additional content sections for wholesale pages -->
            <div class="wholesale-sections">
                <div class="section">
                    <h2>Buying Options</h2>
                    <p>Learn about different wholesale formats including dozen, case, pallet, and container quantities. Each format offers different pricing structures and minimum order requirements.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="section">
                    <h2>Supplier Information</h2>
                    <p>Discover trusted suppliers and sourcing strategies. Learn how to vet suppliers, negotiate terms, and build long-term relationships in the wholesale industry.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="section">
                    <h2>Costs & Pricing</h2>
                    <p>Understand wholesale pricing structures, profit margins, and cost considerations. Learn how to calculate break-even points and maximize profitability.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="section">
                    <h2>Risks & Considerations</h2>
                    <p>Identify potential risks in wholesale operations including quality control, shipping delays, market fluctuations, and regulatory compliance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <% if (relatedPages && relatedPages.length > 0) { %>
    <div class="related-pages">
        <h3>Related Wholesale Guides</h3>
        <ul>
            <% relatedPages.forEach(relatedPage => { %>
                <li><a href="/page/<%= relatedPage.slug %>"><%= relatedPage.title %></a></li>
            <% }); %>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <% } %>
</div>

<style>
.page-content {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.page-meta-info {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.category-link a {
    background: #3498db;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
}

.category-link a:hover {
    background: #2980b9;
}

.page-content h1 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
}

.content {
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.wholesale-sections {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
}

.wholesale-sections .section {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
}

.wholesale-sections h2 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
}

.related-pages {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.related-pages h3 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.related-pages ul {
    list-style: none;
}

.related-pages li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.related-pages a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.related-pages a:hover {
    color: #2980b9;
    text-decoration: underline;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-content h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .wholesale-sections {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .page-meta-info {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }
}
</style>
